      "role": "user",
      "content": "the knight metaphor makes sense for the concept, but can you explain the actual mechanics? like how does the bond between the two materials work so they actually act as one unit? i'm looking for the technical side of how the stress is transferred between the steel and the concrete when a load is applied.",
